既<br />\n不過隻星光大師跑2疊都頂到第2<br />\n隻勁飛勁就真係有點兒唔夠級數<br />\n<br />\n利申allin左10蚊3寶買佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以呢隻真係好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 初出又係吹到一出即勝之後李寶利騎到輸一條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次又吹到大仆街唔放手 講到呢場會贏咁款<br />\n點知又走出黎呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2869cc4ba6e9699e2360b25d72e4f045a1af403","tid":100770,"uid":17527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個post每隔3日一定上番水<br />\n用黎俾班豬馬撚叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係想叫班馬迷提防一埋垃圾呃錢馬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28500c9c15933fe37220a7cc2a133b4f712c11da","tid":100770,"uid":17527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個post每隔3日一定上番水<br />\n用黎俾班豬馬撚叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係想叫班馬迷提防一堆垃圾呃錢馬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5aacd3fe5c2b1a040fb4ecf4f1d1d9ec54d81bfe","tid":100770,"uid":62377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"智愛搭潘狗  伏到仆街"},{"pid":"3c1475446f2abb59b0565e183564d47548592235","tid":100770,"uid":14482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:14:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3276fc6d3979836f19fe64734ed3770b3743e1d5","tid":100770,"uid":56058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"大印偽鈔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e635f233c1bb30ed1dbd63b74033def83a85cf3","tid":100770,"uid":61177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"巴基之星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺尾跑就追唔切<br />\